@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: UMLExecutableElement.java 976 2022-01-06 11:39:58Z tquadrat $") @API(status=INTERNAL, since="0.0.5") public abstract class UMLExecutableElement extends UMLMemberElement implements ExecutableElement
The wrapper for an ExecutableElement instance, enhanced by information needed for the creation of the UML graph.
